Contact me if you would like a specific colour in this style.

I am captivated by these Japanese seed beads!

Featuring an icy green triangular shape seed bead and beautiful magatama seed beads in an egg shell and pale watermelon with a shimmery lustre finish.

Bracelet is one size fits all and the earrings measure 6cm (can be longer or shorter if desired).

Measures approx 20cm.

Note that the beads are a little more lime that shown here, they look slightly mustard(ish) in the pic.

A unique asymmetrical set for day and nightwear.  

This set features Czech glass starburst ovals, glass leaves and metal coated acrylic beads (that look exactly the same as metal without the weight).

The earrings are strung with black cord and measure approx 5cm.

Thanks for looking!

Gorgeous amethyst coloured teardrops, wire wrapped with copper wire (in a silver finish) and a non-tarnish rhodium filigree connector.

Ear wires are nickel free french hooks in antique silver finish.

These are stunning when the light hits them and measure 7cm.

Thanks for looking.

Thanks for looking

A great pair that could be worn throughout the day with jeans, but also perfect for a little black dress.

These ones measure 7cm, have been wire wrapped with copper wire (in an antique silver finish) and are hung on super sturdy nickel free kidney wires.

Thanks for looking.

Citrus seed beads and howlite turquoise nuggets make up these modern boho earrings with gunmetal findings.

Measuring 5cm, these are a gorgeous peach and orange lucite beads that really pick up the sunlight.  Khaki linen cord has been knotted with Czech faceted crystals.

Available in brown, red or pink.

Thanks for looking.

This one of a kind pendant features my own polymer clay birdy, which has been shaped, baked, sanded, painted and glazed by me and sits upon a Czech glass branch.

The chain is super sturdy and by Vintaj Brass Co., it measures approx 34.5cm when held up by the clasp (69cm total).

These ones measure 5.5cm.

Measuring around 3.6cm, these sweet little earrings feature sterling silver ear wires which have been hand forged and hammered by me to form a unique french hook.

Thanks for looking.

name: Floral dangles

Brass bead caps layered, plus lilac seed beads and an aubergine crystal.  Ear wires are nickel free vintage style leverbacks.

They measure 6.5cm.

Thanks for looking.

Peanut shaped Vintaj Brass Co. chain with swooping bird, antique brass branch and Czech glass bellflowers.

A shorter style, collar length (23cm when held up by clasp, or 46cm full length of chain).

Thanks for looking.

Caramel glass baked beads with turquoise ceramic focal, floral glass and ebony nuggets.  Bracelet has a large ornate clasp with floral detail too.

This one measures just over 20cm.

Thanks for looking.

Another polymer clay bird pendant made by me, hung on gunmetal coloured brass cable chain and a cluster of Czech glass bell flowers.

This one measures 34cm when held up by the clasp (68cm total length) and an additional 5cm for the bird and floral pendant.

The bird has been shaped, baked, sanded, painted and glazed by me.

Thanks for looking.

Super chunky wire wrapped earrings with gunmetal etched bars, copper wire in a silver finish and nickel free french hooks in antique silver.

These ones measure nearly 6cm in length, with the turquoise bead measuring 1.8cm in diameter.

Thanks for looking.

Enameled skulls with Rhodium plated charms, which remind me of can can skirts!

These lovelies measure 5cm in total and I only have 2 pairs of this style, one of white, one black!

Thanks for looking.

description:
This unique seashore inspired bracelet features a brass double link chain, howlite rondelles, seed beads and small lampwork glass spacers.

This bracelet measures around 20.5cm, and the charm and the large handforged clasp sits to the front of the hand.

Thanks for looking.

name: Teardrops
description:
Faceted glass teardrops, wire wrapped in non-tarnish brass wire, hung on large kidney wires with peanut-shaped seed beads for extra detail!

These ones measure just short of 6cm.

Thanks for looking.

name: Midnight seashells
description:
These are very cute.  Antique copper chain full of dainty little shells with blue faceted crystals.

They measure approx 5.5cm.

Thanks for looking.

name: Autumn Birdy Necklace
description:
Gorgeous rustic polymer clay bird sits above a ceramic bead that has been dipped in fine silver.  A brass leaf sits underneath, inked in off-white and layered with an antique copper floral bead cap.

This one measures 28cm, when held up by the clasp, 35cm in total including the pendant below.

Thanks for looking.

name: Nouveau style dangles
description:
A really sweet pair of earrings, 5cm long featuring non-tarnish, antique brass round french hooks, inked Art Nouveau style connectors and lilac peanut seed beads. These have been inked by hand.

Lovely detail on these ones.

Thanks for looking.

name: Floral cluster necklace
description:
A medley of flowers hung from a large lucite pendant in champagne, ivory, teal and orange.  Chain is antique brass with a silver finish.

This one measures 28cm, with a further 7cm for the pendant (when held up by the clasp).  From end to end, chain is 56cm.

Thanks for looking.

name: Bellflower dangles
description:
Bursting with colour, these earrings feature a super sturdy ear wire in antique silver (brass) with an abstract (slightly pine cone-ish looking charm), with lime and magenta Czech glass bellflowers.

These lovelies measure 7.cm.

Thanks for looking.

name: Vintage style birdy necklace

Vintage style brass birds, inked with lilac patina on a fine brass chain with soldered links.

This one measures approx 27cm (when held up by the clasp). 54cm total chain with a further 6cm with the pendant.

Thanks for looking.

name: Blossom
description:
A feminine bracelet using howlite rondelles, dusky pink ceramcs and lucite florals.

This one measures 21cm, slightly larger than my usual bracelets (at 20cm).  Can be adjusted if need be.

Thanks for looking.

Nicki

A larger bracelet with gorgeous ceramic ovals that look like pebbles.  Also features copper discs between the links.  Each bead has been wire wrapped for durability.  This has some weight to it and is on the larger size, measures 21.5cm.

Thanks for looking.

name: Ceramic lantern necklace
description:
This is a gorgeous mottled ceramic lantern-shaped bead, hung on Vintaj Brass Co cable chain, which is a lovely chocolatey brown.  The focal bead has been wire wrapped with non-tarnish wire.

The chain measures 60cm (30cm when held up by the clasp).

Thanks for looking.

name: Daisy pendant earrings

Measuring 7cm, these earrings feature antique silver (brass) daisy pendants, Czech glass and nickel free shell lever backs.

Thanks for looking

Ear wires are non-tarnish, french round hooks.  They measure just over 5cm.

Thanks for looking.

name: Rustic Florals

Huge fan of the rustic picasso style beads, shown here in a mottled green.  Lucite and glass bellflowers in emerald, dark coral and white on gorgeous non-tarnish, round french hooks.

These ones measure approx 5cm.

Thanks for looking.

description:
Love this colour combination.  it's a variation on the Gardenia bracelet.

Handmade lampwork beads, rubber O rings and a gorgeous vintage style copper button on the Vintaj Brass leaf focal.

Measuring approx 20cm.

Thanks for looking.

name: Turquoise Patina Leaf Earrings
description:
Measuring approx. 5cm, these are a gorgeous colour.  Vinaj Arte Metal leaves have been inked and sanded and are suspended from a light violet crystal.

Ear wires are nickel free.

Thanks for looking.

name: Starbust waterlilly

Measuring 20cm, features hammered brass starburst focal with Czech glass flower in turquoise.

Thanks for looking.

description:
Gorgeous handmade glass beads hung on wishbone style sterling silver ear wires.

An modern style, bursting with colour!  Just one pair available.

Thanks for looking.

name: Butterfly filigrees
description:
Measuring 4.5cm, these lovely butterflies have been painted and sanded for a faux patina.  Preciosa crystals added in lilac and they're hung on antique copper kidney wires.

These look lovely on, I have a soft spot for the inked metals!

Thanks for looking.

An earthy bracelet with a mix of ceramics, lucite, ebony wood and coral.

Measures 20cm and has teeny seed beads inside the toggle bard.  

Thanks for looking.

A beautiful vintage style chain by Vintaj Brass Co holds a handmade earthenware pendant (made by me) with a celadon glaze.  The pendant measures just under 3cm.  Note that it is glazed on both sides, apart from the inside of the ring of which the flower sits inside.

Thanks for looking.

description:
A one of a kind bracelet made with my own earthenware toggle in a Celadon glaze and jasper, glass and ebony wood.

Measures 20.5cm and the toggle sits to the front of the hand.

Note that the ceramic toggle is slightly greener than it looks in the pic.

Thanks for looking

name: Locked Up

A great pair of earrings featuring Vintaj Arte Metal hearts which have been inked in turquoise and sanded lightly.

These ones measure 5.5cm.  Can be inked off white if you prefer.

Thanks for looking.

Love this feminine bracelet!

The chain is a sturdy bronze large link, I have wire wrapped the sides with red coral tube beads, and the red floral beads are lucite, finished with vintage pixies, rubber O rings and ornate clasp.

Measures 20cm. Can be made smaller or larger on request.

Thanks for looking!

name: Shrinking Violet Bracelet
description:
Gorgeous colours in this asymmetrical bracelet.

It measures just over 20cm and features artisan glass with violet seed beads and beautiful multi link antique copper chain.

description:
A unique antique copper necklace with ceramic focal bead in the shape of a little vase.  Also features, handmade glass spacers, and antique copper findings.

This one measures approx 31cm in length to the top of the pendant, with the pendant taking up another 4.5cm.  

Thanks for looking!

Beautiful ceramic cubes have been wire wrapped with antique brass non-tarnish wire and finished with a strip of leather for an unusual combination.

A great spring/summer daywear bracelet.  Ceramics are off white with blue, brown, green a a small amount of dusky pink.


Thanks for looking.

A simple, yet striking bracelet made with red (recycled) sea glass, peach stone, ceramic rings and artisan lampwork glass.

This one is a little smaller than usual and measures just under 20cm.

Thanks for looking.

This one measures 20cm and is perfect with jeans!

Thanks for looking!

Measures just over 20cm.

Thanks for looking!

Sorry, that name made me giggle!

Gorgeous mauve glass seed beads, unusual lucite coin beads in turquoise and chocolate and an artisan-made glass bead as the focal of the asymmetrical detail.

A really nice short, feminine necklace.

Thanks for looking.

One size fits all.  Gorgeous Czech picasso flowers on memory wire with howlite turquoise.

 A nice boho feel to this one.

Thanks for looking.

Czech glass leaves have been wire wrapped with copper wire (in antique silver finish) and are hung on Trinity Brass kidney wires, which are super sturdy.  Teeny peanut-shaped seed beads sit on the kidney wire.  

These lovelies measure 6.5cm.

I love this floral connector!

A simple, unique bracelet constructed with 'Vintaj' and 'Fallen Angel Brass' which is beautiful quality and chocolate in colour.  The floral focal is a really sturdy filigree that has been curved to the natural shape of the wrist. 

Also features a small handmade glass droplet in lime and sea sediment jasper in magenta.

Fastens at the front of the hand.  

Thanks for looking.

These are sweet.  An olive faceted glass bead has been wire wrapped and is hung from a unique embossed connector and painted with turquoise patina ink.

They measure 4cm and ear wires are nickel and lead free - Vintaj Brass.

Thanks for looking.

A simple, elegant pair of earrings with genuine Swarovski bicones. They're rhodium plated (non-tarnish) and there's just one pair of these lovelies as I had to keep a pair for my own jewellery box ; )

They measure 6cm - thank you for looking!

This is a one of a kind bracelet made with genuine vintage components.  Love the little corn style beads in a dark yellow.  The clear connector and white spikey flowers are also vintage finds.

Rubber O rings and freshwater pearls have also been used on this bracelet.  It measures approx 20cm.

Thanks for looking!

A unique pair of earrings measuring 7cm, these earrings have lots of detail and mix fluted glass, with faceted crystals, gunmetal and transparent lime seed beads and opaque picasso ovals in mottled green.

They're hung on Trinity Brass shell leverbacks in antique silver.

Thanks for looking.

A simple, feminine ceramic bracelet made with pastel elongated oval ceramics, brass batik style beads in antique silver and peach rubber O rings.

Measures approx 21cm.

This would make a lovely gift!!

Thanks for looking.

These are really sweet.  Vintaj Brass filigrees have been painted and sealed with a very subtle pearl/metallic green patina and topped off with a burnt orange crystal.

They measure 6cm. (note that they are the original chocolatey brass colour on the back, but can be painted metallic if you prefer).

Thanks for looking.

They are embossed and left as raw brass on the back (can be painted on the back on request, if you prefer).

They measure 7cm.

Pendant is carved wood and measures 5cm wide.  Gorgeous peanut shaped seed beads have been used for a nice touch and wire wrapped to finish.

Chain is antique brass, etched.

Thanks for looking.

A unique style, and a great gift for Xmas.

Thanks for looking!

Thanks for looking.

Dont forget to like my page at facebook/littleredheadjewellery to go into the draw for my MONTHLY GIVEAWAY

These earrings have been wire wrapped with copper wire (in a silver finish) and ear wires are gunmetal toned to match the bars.

thanks for looking.

nicki
